<p>Despite her medical hurdles, Lyric's strength has not waned and she knows she's a queen just like her idol.</p>

<p>In a video her mom said she was so shocked that Beyonce had sent the gift but Lyric knows her worth. </p>

<p>'You know why? Cause I'm a queen,' the starlet in training said. 'She says she only gives things to queens and I'm a queen.'</p>

